{
  "$defs": {
    "SimClock": {
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "description": "仿真时钟（task5 双时间戳地基）：边缘仿真器(SUMO)的自有时钟，与 envelope.time.event_ts\n(挂钟)并存，作为异步控制回路的对齐/过期判据。完整的世界-边缘时钟同步留作未来一等公民问题。",
      "properties": {
        "sim_time": {
          "minimum": 0,
          "title": "Sim Time",
          "type": "number"
        },
        "sim_step": {
          "minimum": 0,
          "title": "Sim Step",
          "type": "integer"
        }
      },
      "required": [
        "sim_time",
        "sim_step"
      ],
      "title": "SimClock",
      "type": "object"
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "description": "交通域全局总览（task5 P-10，topic anp.traffic.status.global.v1）。\n\n系统级 model 聚合所有路口观测产出的**共识指标**（路口数/车辆/等待/均速）；SV 仿真元信息\n（算法/步数/运行状态）不在此，由 SV host 经心跳 ``metadata`` 带、网关合并（保持「共识由系统级算」）。",
  "properties": {
    "status_type": {
      "const": "traffic.global",
      "default": "traffic.global",
      "title": "Status Type",
      "type": "string"
    },
    "junction_count": {
      "minimum": 0,
      "title": "Junction Count",
      "type": "integer"
    },
    "total_vehicles": {
      "minimum": 0,
      "title": "Total Vehicles",
      "type": "integer"
    },
    "total_halting": {
      "minimum": 0,
      "title": "Total Halting",
      "type": "integer"
    },
    "mean_speed_kmh": {
      "minimum": 0,
      "title": "Mean Speed Kmh",
      "type": "number"
    },
    "sim_clock": {
      "anyOf": [
        {
          "$ref": "#/$defs/SimClock"
        },
        {
          "type": "null"
        }
      ],
      "default": null
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "junction_count",
    "total_vehicles",
    "total_halting",
    "mean_speed_kmh"
  ],
  "title": "交通域全局总览 payload（task5 P-10）",
  "type": "object",
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema"
}
